objects.description: [FIN6](https://attack.mitre.org/group/G0037) has used [Windows Credential Editor](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0005) for credential dumping, as well as Metasploit’s [PsExec](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0029) NTDSGRAB module to obtain a copy of the victim's Active Directory database.

external_references.description: FireEye Threat Intelligence. (2016, April). Follow the Money: Dissecting the Operations of the Cyber Crime Group FIN6. Retrieved June 1, 2016.
